Body: Description: User is trying to upload file to docusign.upload.com file is getting stuck, browser keeps buffering. No block logs are showing on EPP console, when gave EPP suspension OTP everything works fine.
What We've Learned Updated: EPP Client blocked a file upload to docusign.com, but it did not generate any block log
Next Steps Updated: 15.05.2025: A remote session will be scheduled in order to investigate and collect a set of logs
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Emil Podar, Om Bankar
